Thinkful blog project
Directory structure:

blog                        Root directory
├── blog                    Module directory
│   ├── static              Static files directory
│   │   └── css             Stylesheets directory
│   ├── templates           Templates directory
│   ├── config.py           App configuration options
│   ├── database.py         Database setup
│   ├── filters.py          Custom Jinja filters
│   ├── __init__.py         App setup and configuration
│   ├── models.py           SQLAlchemy models
│   ├── views.py            Views
├── env                     Virtualenv
├── manage.py               App management file
├── requirements.txt        Install requirements

Commands to execute:

1. Move into the root directory - "cd blog"
2. Set up the virtualenv - "virtualenv env"
3. Activate the virtualenv - "source env/bin/activate"
4. Install the dependencies - "pip install flask sqlalchemy flask-login flask-script flask-migrate mistune"
5. Freeze the dependencies - "pip freeze > requirements.txt"
6. Ignore the virtualenv - "echo env > .gitignore"
